reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great small bag!
reviews.reviewText: Attractive, light weight bag with plenty of compartments to keep you organized! I have two larger backpack style bags, but wanted a smaller one for every day. Finding the right hands-free sling type bag that looks stylish was not easy, but this one is perfect! Looks high-quality, well-made, and is comfortable wearing cross-body for long periods of time. This one is a winner!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great stylish purse!
reviews.reviewText: I bought this after seeing along bags become popular again. I love this! It’s big enough to hold my iPhone 13max and has two zipper compartments to hold enough basic stuff. The color is true to the image. It’s good quality and the strap is comfortable and sits well over the shoulder! I can’t wait to continue mixing and matching it with more outfits!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great little purse
reviews.reviewText: I love this purse and so do my daughter and daughter-in-law. It is the perfect size for a phone, credit card, $, glasses , and a couple of additional things. Great when you don’t want to carry a large purse. It also looks great, is light, and it sits nicely on the body.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great sling bag!
reviews.reviewText: This is my second order. I have owned and used a black (size large) version of this bag for two years now and it is still in good shape! I initially purchased it for traveling but I kept using it every day since then. When I needed a brown purse to match a new pair of boots, I immediately thought about getting the same sling bag! It carries all my essentials and never falls off my shoulder. Everything is well organized inside and it does contain a lot of stuff! The only thing I would complain about is about rain protection, the inside of the bag gets wet through the zipper... but to be fair, it only happened to me once and the rain was pouring heavily! I have sprayed the zipper fabric with water repellent and it helped. The zippers are metallic and slide smoothly. I like that I can change side depending on how I want to carry the bag; across the right shoulder, the left shoulder or just on the shoulder like a regular purse. The bag always stays right up too. I also purchased a small size in light blue, but it barely held my phone (the zipper was rubbing against it while closing) Now that I have a larger phone, I can't use it anymore. Make sure you check measurements when picking the right size for you!
